  "lyrics": "Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh\nNo matter where you go\nNo matter how you try to hide, baby\nI said no matter where you are\nI'm gonna find you from the earth to the sea\nOh, well, oh, well, oh, well, oh, such a perfect summer light\nYou appear in between sights\nWith a blink you vanish left this lightning in me\nHeart flash, I gotta find you, return this spark\nNo matter where you go\nNo matter how you try to hide, baby\nI said no matter where you are\nI'm gonna find you from the earth to the sea\nYou told me you loved me forever\nNow I need to find the coroner\nTo tell me if I'm alive\nYou left with all my heart\nNow you're gonna know what juice and me\nThink on the brink\nThere's no denying you can't leave me\nWe should end together\nI've got these pills and a vengeance towards you\nCome on, get together, chill\nNo matter where you go\nNo matter how you try to hide, baby\nNo matter where you are\nYou know I'm gonna find you, yeah, from the earth to the sea\nNo matter\nNo matter how you try, baby\nNo matter where you go and where you are\nI'm gonna find you from the earth to the sea\nOh, so don't run, cutie, don't run",
